### Get all movies
GET http://localhost:3000/movies

###

### Filter movies by year
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=2010

###

### Filter movies by director (partial match, case-insensitive)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?director=Nolan

###

### Filter movies by title (partial match, case-insensitive)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?title=matrix

###

### Filter movies by year and director (combined filters)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=2010&director=Christopher Nolan

###

### Filter movies by year and title (combined filters)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=1999&title=Matrix

###

### Filter movies by all three parameters
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=2010&director=Nolan&title=Inception

###

### Filter with no matching results
GET http://localhost:3000/movies?year=1950

###

### Get a specific movie by ID (existing movie)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/1

###

### Get a specific movie by ID (non-existent movie)
GET http://localhost:3000/movies/999

###

### Create a new movie (valid)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Shawshank Redemption",
  "director": "Frank Darabont",
  "year": 1994
}

###

### Create a new movie (valid - upcoming release)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Five Nights at Freddy's",
  "director": "Scott Cawthon",
  "year": 2023
}

###

### Create a new movie (missing required fields - should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Incomplete Movie"
}

###

### Create a new movie (empty strings - should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "director": "",
  "year": 2020
}

###

### Create a new movie (invalid year - not a number - should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Invalid Year Movie",
  "director": "Test Director",
  "year": "not-a-number"
}

###

### Create a new movie (invalid year - before 1888 - should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Too Old Movie",
  "director": "Ancient Director",
  "year": 1800
}

###

### Create a new movie (invalid year - too far in future - should fail)
POST http://localhost:3000/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Future Movie",
  "director": "Future Director",
  "year": 2040
}

###

### Update an existing movie (valid - update all fields)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception (Updated)",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan (Updated)",
  "year": 2011
}

###

### Update an existing movie (valid - partial update)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Matrix Reloaded"
}

###

### Update an existing movie (valid - update year only)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "year": 2011
}

###

### Update a movie (non-existent ID - should fail with 404)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Does Not Exist",
  "director": "Nobody",
  "year": 2020
}

###

### Update a movie (invalid year - should fail with 400)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "year": "invalid"
}

###

### Update a movie (empty title - should fail with 400)
PUT http://localhost:3000/movies/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": ""
}

###

### Delete a movie (existing - should return 204)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/movies/3

###

### Delete a movie (non-existent - should fail with 404)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/movies/999

